Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We shared our hopes, we shared our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:56.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I miss him more than I realized
